org.forgerock.openam.session.service.access.persistence

Interface InternalSessionStoreStep

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInternalSessionStoreStep, InMemoryInternalSessionCacheStep, SessionPersistenceManagerStep, TimeOutSessionFilterStep

    public interface InternalSessionStoreStep
    A step in persisting a session. Each method has access to a following step to continue if necessary.
